Package medicinemanagements

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    InventoryManagementControl
    The InventoryManagementControl class manages the inventory of medicines in the system.
    Medicine
    The Medicine class represents a medicine in the inventory.
    ReplenishmentRequest
    The ReplenishmentRequest class represents a request to replenish stock for a specific medicine.
    ReplenishmentRequestManagementControl
    The ReplenishmentRequestManagementControl class manages the handling of replenishment requests for medicines.
    RequestCreateControl
    The RequestCreateControl class is responsible for creating replenishment requests for medicines.
